The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 The City Diary

 One man was killed and four others were injured after being run over by a truck, belonging to Congress councillor of ward six Suman Singh, on Cossipore Road, near Chitpur railway quarters, on Tuesday evening. Police said the truck lost control and mounted a pavement before hitting the pedestrians.

